    "song_title_zh": "",
    "song_id": "08-right-hand-man",
    "line_index": "52",
    "english": "How can I keep leading when the people I'm",
    "ipa": "/haʊ kæn aɪ kip lidɪŋ wɛn ðə pipəl aɪm/",
    "chinese_translation": "我领导的那帮人全在撤退，",
