    "english": "Elizabeth Schuyler It's a pleasure to meet you",
    "ipa": "/ᵻlɪzəbəθ ʃaɪlɚɹ ɪts ɐ plɛʒɚ tə mit ju/",
    "chinese_translation": "伊丽莎白•斯凯勒，很高兴认识你",
