    "song_title_zh": "",
    "song_id": "23-non-stop",
    "line_index": "181",
    "english": "Look around, look around at how lucky we are to be alive right now",
    "ipa": "/lʊk ɚɹaʊnd lʊk ɚɹaʊnd æt haʊ lʌki wi ɑɹ təbi ɐlaɪv ɹaɪt naʊ/",
    "chinese_translation": "看看周围，看看我们活着一路走到现在是多么幸运",
