    "song_id": "24-what-d-i-miss",
    "line_index": "49",
    "english": "I just got home and now I'm headed up to New York",
    "ipa": "/aɪ dʒʌst ɡɑt hoʊm ænd naʊ aɪm hɛdᵻd ʌp tə nu jɔɹk/",
    "chinese_translation": "我刚到家，现在便要前往纽约",
