    "song_title": "What'd I Miss",
    "song_title_zh": "",
    "song_id": "24-what-d-i-miss",
    "line_index": "58",
    "english": "My friend James Madison, red in the face",
    "ipa": "/maɪ fɹɛnd dʒeɪmz mædɪsən ɹɛd ɪnðə feɪs/",
    "chinese_translation": "我的朋友詹姆斯·麦迪森满脸通红",
