    "song_title": "What'd I Miss",
    "song_title_zh": "",
    "song_id": "24-what-d-i-miss",
    "line_index": "66",
    "english": "Hamilton's new financial plan is nothing less",
    "ipa": "/hæməltənz nu faɪnænʃəl plæn ɪz nʌθɪŋ lɛs/",
    "chinese_translation": "汉密尔顿的新财政策略",
