    "song_id": "28-the-room-where-it-happens",
    "line_index": "140",
    "english": "Dark as a tomb where it happens",
    "ipa": "/dɑɹk æz ɐ tum wɛɹ ɪt hæpənz/",
    "chinese_translation": "如坟墓般密不透光的决策现场",
