    "song_id": "46-who-lives-who-dies-who-tells-your-story",
    "line_index": "60",
    "english": "And when my time is up, have I done enough?",
    "ipa": "/ænd wɛn maɪ taɪm ɪz ʌp hæv aɪ dʌn ɪnʌf/",
    "chinese_translation": "而我离开时是否可以满足期望",
