    "song_id": "46-who-lives-who-dies-who-tells-your-story",
    "line_index": "61",
    "english": "Will they tell our story? (Will they tell your story?)",
    "ipa": "/wɪl ðeɪ tɛl aʊɚ stɔɹi wɪl ðeɪ tɛl jʊɹ stɔɹi/",
